fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.data.mapdb.util

Class MapDbURI

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.emf.common.util.URI
      • fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.util.PersistenceURI
        • fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.data.mapdb.util.MapDbURI

  • public class MapDbURI
extends PersistenceURI
    A specific PersistenceURI that creates MapDB specific resource URIs from a File descriptor or an existing URI.

    The class defines a MapDB specific URI scheme that is used to register MapDbPersistenceBackendFactory in PersistenceBackendFactoryRegistry and configure the protocol-to-factory map of an existing ResourceSet with a PersistentResourceFactory.

    See Also:
    PersistenceBackendFactoryRegistry, MapDbPersistenceBackendFactory, PersistentResourceFactory
